sections.markdown: # How long does it take us to resolve issues?

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "DAVIS_PROBLEM"
| summarize by:{bin(timestamp, 1m)}, avg(toDouble(resolved_problem_duration) / 60000), alias:minutes_to_resolve

sections.markdown: # So which problem types take the longest to resolve?

sections.title: Problem resolution time by event category

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "DAVIS_PROBLEM"
| summarize by:{bin(timestamp, 1m), event.category}, avg(toDouble(resolved_problem_duration) / 60000), alias:minutes_to_resolve
